osing_date": "2026-07-12"}}, {"model": "myApp.jobpostcontent", "pk": 1, "fields": {"job": 1, "topic_title": "Job Description", "title_level": "H2", "description": "SJS Company is seeking a reliable, responsible, and professional Driver to join our team on a temporary full-time basis. The successful candidate will be responsible for the safe and timely transportation of goods, documents, or staff members (depending on assignment requirements) while maintaining high standards of professionalism and road safety.\r\n\r\nThe role requires someone who is punctual, trustworthy, and able to work independently with minimal supervision. You will play a key part in ensuring smooth daily operations by supporting transportation and delivery needs across different locations within Mpumalanga and surrounding areas.", "format_type": "paragraph"}}, {"model": "myApp.jobpostcontent", "pk": 2, "fields": {"job": 1, "topic_title": "Key Responsibilities", "title_level": "H2", "description": "Safely transport goods, documents, or staff to designated locations\r\nEnsure all deliveries and pickups are completed on time\r\nPerform daily vehicle inspections before and after trips\r\nMaintain cleanliness and proper care of the assigned vehicle\r\nReport any mechanical issues or accidents immediately\r\nFollow all traffic laws and company driving policies\r\nKeep accurate trip logs, fuel records, and delivery confirmations\r\nAssist with loading and offloading when required\r\nMaintain professional communication with clients and staff", "format_type": "bullet"}}, {"model": "myApp.jobpostcontent", "pk": 3, "fields": {"job": 1, "topic_title": "Minimum Requirements", "title_level": "H3", "description": "Valid South African driver’s license (Code 8/10/14 depending on vehicle type)\r\nProven driving experience (at least 1–2 years preferred)\r\nGood knowledge of Mpumalanga routes and surrounding areas\r\nClean driving record (no serious traffic violations)\r\nAbility to work flexible hours, including overtime if needed\r\nBasic literacy skills (able to read maps, instructions, and fill log sheets)\r\nPhysically fit and able to assist with loading/unloading if required", "format_type": "bullet"}}, {"model": "myApp.jobpostcontent", "pk": 4, "fields": {"job": 1, "topic_title": "Required Skills & Attributes", "title_level": "H2", "description": "Strong sense of responsibility and reliability\r\nExcellent time management skills\r\nGood communication and interpersonal skills\r\nAbility to work under pressure and meet deadlines\r\nAttention to detail and safety awareness\r\nHonest, disciplined, and professional behavior\r\nProblem-solving ability in unexpected road situations", "format_type": "bullet"}}, {"model": "myApp.jobpostcontent", "pk": 5, "fields": {"job": 1, "topic_title": "Enquiries", "title_level": "H3", "description": "For more information or to apply for this position, please contact:\r\n\r\nSJS Company Recruitment Team\r\n📧 Email: careers@sjscompany.co.za\r\n\r\n📞 Phone: 013 XXX XXXX (Mpumalanga Office)\r\n📍 Office Hours: Monday – Friday, 08:00 – 16:30", "format_type": "bullet"}}, {"model": "myApp.jobapplication", "pk": 15, "fields": {"user": 25, "job": 1, "status": "approved", "date_applied": "2026-06-28T14:15:55.002Z"}}, {"model": "myApp.jobapplication", "pk": 16, "fields": {"user": 29, "job": 1, "status": "accepted", "date_applied": "2026-06-28T14:37:01.461Z"}}, {"model": "myApp.herophoto", "pk": 1, "fields": {"page": "home", "image": "hero_photos/home_pic2.png"}}, {"model": "myApp.herophoto", "pk": 2, "fields": {"page": "about", "image": "hero_photos/truck.png"}}, {"model": "myApp.herophoto", "pk": 3, "fields": {"page": "services", "image": "hero_photos/chair_product.jpg"}}, {"model": "myApp.herophoto", "pk": 4, "fields": {"page": "careers", "image": "hero_photos/hands_shaking.png"}}, {"model": "myApp.herophoto", "pk": 5, "fields": {"page": "contact", "image": "hero_photos/phone_in_hand.png"}}, {"model": "myApp.homehero", "pk": 1, "fields": {"title": 